\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of my biggest sins when I was a kid\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}08 - Smoked a cigarette \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}13 - Ran away from school\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}17 \'96 totaled my dad\'92s truck\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}College \'96 Well I\'92m not going to tell you what I did in college but it was worse!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  You were the same way right?\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you were a kid you did things and thought it was the end of the world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Then you got a little older and realized it wasn\'92t that big of a deal\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}only to do something else that you in turn thought was the end of the world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in a room like this week probably have some pretty bad things done.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In a room like this week have people who have stolen things, cheated others, hurt other, abused others \'96 physically, emotionally, sexually, we have addicts and people who think they\'92ve gone too far from God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Or maybe it isn\'92t a moment but a seasons of life, or maybe even seasons where you just walked away from God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know what your issue, thing, season, or past is\'85what I can promise you is that it isn\'92t the single worst thing you can do in life!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  Today I want to tell you about what I believe is the single worst thing you can do in life, but before we get there we have to look at greatest thing you can do\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This morning we\'92re going to start in John 15 and Jesus is talking to His disciples and He makes this statement\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 12\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub My command is this: Love each other as I have loved you.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Greater love has no one than this: to lay down one\'92s life for one\'92s 
\f4\i friends
\f3\i0 .  John 15\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus, not me, says the greatest thing you can do for someone is to die for them.  More specifically He says the greatest thing is to die for your friends.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have different level of friends but your spouse can be your friend\'85etc\'85.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why we honor veterans and people who give their life for others\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  So, Jesus proves what He says\'85if you\'92re not familiar with the story He gives His life for his friends and dies on the cross\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That is why we are here today\'85to celebrate the death and resurrection of Jesus and what He did for all of us.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  But what you may not know is that in the middle of dying for his \'91Friends\'92\'85His best friend is denying Him.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That\'92s right, Jesus is dying for Peter and Peter is over there telling other people he doesn\'92t know who Jesus or even want to be associated with the man\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Luke tells the story this way\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 60\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Peter replied, \'93Man, I don\'92t know what you\'92re talking about!\'94 Just as he was speaking, the rooster crowed.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In one of the other texts it says he was cussing up a storm at a teenage girl about how offended he was that she would think he would ever associate with such a man!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 61\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The Lord\'a0turned and looked straight at Peter.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ever had that moment when you get caught\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Or you just are confronted with all your junk at the same time\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This feeling of complete betrayal of someone who trusted you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This has to be the single worst thing a person can do!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf5 The proximity of the relationship determines the power of the pain!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now if I\'92m Jesus I\'92m done aren\'92t you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Peter should know better\'85it\'92s His best friend!!!!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  But if you know the story then you know Jesus still goes to the cross and dies for us all\'85even Peter!\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf4 Christ died for our sins\'a0according to the Scriptures,\'a0
\f5\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub that he was buried,\'a0that he was raised\'a0on the third day according to the Scriptures,  1 Cor 15:3-4\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:   But there is still a problem\'85Peter denied Him, in front of everyone\'85and this is what I want you all to see\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Simon Peter, Thomas\'a0(also known as Didymus
\fs15 \super [b]
\fs24 \nosupersub ), Nathanael\'a0from Cana in Galilee,\'a0the sons of Zebedee,\'a0and two other disciples were together.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So the gang is together hanging out\'85and Peter says\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93I\'92m going out to fish,\'94 Simon Peter told them, and they said, \'93We\'92ll go with you.\'94 So they went out and got into the boat, but that night they caught nothing.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I just want to pause for a second here\'85if Peter is fishing\'85what is He not doing? \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Following Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s given up, it\'92s over.  He tried his best\'85and failed.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And not only did he fail but he betrayed his best friend.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not only did he betray his best friend but Jesus looked right at him when he did it as if to say I know.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So Peter is done and this is where some of you are at today.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve feel as though you failed in following God and so you\'92ve gone back to a previous way of life.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You went back to the drugs or the girls/guys\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You quit going to church and praying because it didn\'92t seem to help\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You were once really close to God but now He seems distant.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re Peter!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Early in the morning, Jesus stood on the shore, but the disciples did not realize that it was Jesus.  
\f0\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He called out to them,\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How would you call out to them\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What name or adjective would you have for you best friend who abandoned you when you needed him most and literally left you to die.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \'93
\f6\i\b Friends
\f1\i0\b0 , haven\'92t you any fish?\'94  John 21\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Friends!!!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus tells them the greatest thing a person can is die for their friends and then Peter does the worst thing imaginable and Jesus looks at him and calls him\'85FRIEND!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know what you think you\'92ve done, are doing, or can\'92t stop doing to make you not good enough or God but you never were a part of the solution to begin with.\
