\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  The problem we struggle with is we\'92ve been told there is a scale.  And on one side there is the good stuff and on the other there is the bad stuff.  \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But there is no scale there is only stains.  \
